Raccoon.RM 
 
Class DBConnection 
 
java.lang.Object
    Raccoon.RM.DBConnection 
 
   Direct Known Subclasses:     DB2LoadDriver ,  InformixLoadDriver ,  SQLLoadDriver  
    public abstract class  DBConnection  extends java.lang.Object    
    DBConnection:   An abstract class to work 
 as the a driver of database. Different types of 
 DBMSs have to implement different drivers.
  
 Notice, do not import com.mysql.jdbc.* 
 or you will have problems!
  

  
    Author:  
   Qi Zhong 
   





  
     
